{"tid":1796903,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"講左幾撚多次出黎野餐要自備雞蛋，罐裝咖啡","createTime":"2019-12-25T03:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-01T05:32:40.000Z","uid":60662,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"880e1f4e9915307c5ca3936404f202dd3e7888f3","tid":1796903,"uid":60662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T03:47:29.000Z","msg":"講撚左出黎野餐要自備雞蛋，罐裝咖啡<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1679134/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1679134/page/1</a><br />\n今次有幾多個人有帶有用？<br />\n如果每個人有一隻蛋一罐咖啡，一開始班剩係有面罩既仲會唔會打得咁開心？<br />\n<br />\n今時今日仲覺得有人會代你救人？有人會代你擋？有人會代你衝？有人會代你掟？<br />\n你連咁低風險既野都唔敢做，你出黎唔好再叫反抗，係班狗面前咪撚叫人仆街死全家<br />\n<br />\n自己諗"},{"pid":"2c2361cc687acb354f152a9e5e165475df157e5d","tid":1796903,"uid":60662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:12:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afdbc264784bf29aafdb56e32ef80fd9cf7627c2","tid":1796903,"uid":77717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:14:42.000Z","msg":"每人兩罐，一個打狗，一個救人"},{"pid":"357581971483653387dfc9770ae9354df563b64a","tid":1796903,"uid":275524,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"afdbc264784bf29aafdb56e32ef80fd9cf7627c2","tid":1796903,"uid":77717,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:14:42.000Z","msg":"每人兩罐，一個打狗，一個救人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:16:13.000Z","msg":"狗只係一個代理人身份"},{"pid":"db1629cf779ac5d8ac6980bfa1f7ef4e69afd7a8","tid":1796903,"uid":195867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:18:53.000Z","msg":"天氣熱阿 買定兩罐可樂放係袋啦"},{"pid":"c2e38a30add37285b1d71c6b64910b66e81b6d4b","tid":1796903,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T04:24:37.000Z","msg":"咪係煙火機 自己食啦<br />\n<br />\n記者都識食煙啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\